{
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "──第11周的早晨。\n龙姐的身体已经变化到没有施术就无法安定下来的程度。"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "（第11周...快满三个月了。龙姐的身体，已经被彻底开发了。）"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "",
      "triggerWeeklySettlement": true
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "（很顺利...多亏了龙姐，经营也稳定了下来。）"
    },
    {
      "character": "",
      "hideCharacter": true,
      "text": "",
      "playSE": "door_chime"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "angry",
      "text": "...来了。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "龙姐！今天也...诶，看起来心情不太好啊。"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "angry",
      "text": "...啊。都怪你。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "surprised",
      "text": "诶？怪我？"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "embarrassed",
      "text": "...前阵子。正在教训手下的时候...突然想起了你的施术。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "surprised",
      "text": "教训手下的时候...？"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "angry",
      "text": "对。然后...手就...变软了。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "embarrassed",
      "text": "手下还说'大姐，您今天好温柔啊'...妈的。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "（教训都变温柔了...到底有多想施术的事啊...）"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "angry",
      "text": "堂堂组织的老大，工作的时候在想那种事...真是的。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "smile",
      "text": "那说明我的施术确实很有效果呢。"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "embarrassed",
      "text": "...啧。别得意。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "...不过说真的。真的很严重。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "严重？"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "embarrassed",
      "text": "...光看到这家店的招牌...身体就...有反应了。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "surprised",
      "text": "光看到招牌就？"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "对。前阵子，车从这里经过...下面就开始发痒...",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "embarrassed",
      "text": "司机还说'大姐，您脸好红啊'...简直是噩梦。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "（完全就是巴甫洛夫的狗...条件反射发情了...）"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "angry",
      "text": "你到底对我做了什么...？",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "smile",
      "text": "我什么都没做啊。是龙姐的身体自己记住了我的施术而已。"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "embarrassed",
      "text": "...啧。记住...不是那个意思...",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "但这说明你的身体变得很诚实了啊。"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "...太诚实了才是问题啊...该死...",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "embarrassed",
      "text": "...还有。还有更严重的事...",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "normal",
      "text": "更严重的？"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "...光听到你的声音...身体就变热了。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "surprised",
      "text": "光听声音就？"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "embarrassed",
      "text": "对。前阵子打电话预约的时候...一听到你的声音...",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "...当场就...下面湿了...",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "（光听声音就湿了...到底被开发到什么程度了...）"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "angry",
      "text": "开会的时候接到电话那次...简直是噩梦。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "embarrassed",
      "text": "一听到你的声音，身体就猛地一颤...",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "在手下们面前...脸涨得通红...只能挂掉电话...",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "smile",
      "text": "那...真是抱歉了。"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "angry",
      "text": "你那脸完全没有抱歉的样子！",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "player",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "（但是，她这么想着我...真的很开心。）"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "embarrassed",
      "text": "...所以说。今天...好好给我施术。",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
    },
    {
      "character": "龙姐",
      "expression": "shy",
      "text": "再这样下去...作为组织的老大...威严都没了...",
      "characterImage": "tatsu/tatsu.png"
